<plot>Sadie, an ambitious clerk is held up late one night at the bookstore where she works. The problem is that no one sees the crime and the thief steals the only video surveillance tape. Each person recounts a different version of what happens adding layers of confusion until nothing is clear. It is only when the surveillance video is screened that the truth is revealed.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?598092</url></doc>
